<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>眼斑公社</title><link>https://wxrss.reinject.top/01051dbf286e24f17cf0a45867091e97/</link><description>An RSS feed.</description><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 23 Feb 2025 09:11:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><generator>wxrss -- https://github.com/0xlane/wxrss</generator><item><title>速看！那些你从未见过的大师 “神龟” 画作，保证你没有见过！</title><link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUzNjk5MjAyMQ==&amp;mid=2247488536&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=af846c3ffea75433cdab6ce7bf0e4332&amp;chksm=fba8e3937cf7745a54056ed7c71596448582a13f673fa67f1219dfec7511e6d33fb97bc01d13&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd</link><description><![CDATA[别好奇为啥咱们的大师能把龟画得如此精妙。咱追求的是修身养性的生活。闲暇时，悠然摇着折扇，自在地骑马赏景，养几只龟，兴致一来就提笔作画。在这过程中，心态始终平和，日子过得闲适又恬淡，不被荣辱之事所扰。就]]></description><author>眼斑公社</author><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 09:20:00 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>开春又可以喂眼斑龟了</title><link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUzNjk5MjAyMQ==&amp;mid=2247488494&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=86cd5a9ef86a6556d517e31092c07aa8&amp;chksm=fbfd9f0e38c192e52ffe08ec5bd1d3335967fbc2e340b75f2f84728941263b215a60db41bd0e&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd</link><description><![CDATA[开春又可以喂眼斑龟了#眼斑龟 #四眼龟 #水龟 #金钱龟 #蛋龟]]></description><author>眼斑公社</author><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 16:26:55 +0800</pubDate></item></channel></rss>